(79, 'widget_text', 'a:5:{i:1;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:379:\"<strong><h5 style=\"color:#ffffff\">About Us</h5></strong> \r\n[gdlr_core_space height=\"21px\"]\r\nWe are safari tour operator based in Uganda and very passionate about East Africa - its nature, wildlife, landscape and cultural diversity. <br><br>\r\n\r\nOur trademark is to design personalized, tailor-made and detailed itineraries for individual and group <a href=\"about-us\">read more</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;s:6:\"visual\";b:0;}i:2;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:608:\"<h5 style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Contact Info</h5>\r\nAddress : Ground floor Buddo House, Bombo road .\r\n\r\nP.O Box 35744\r\nKampala, Uganda [gdlr_core_space height=\"-13px\"]\r\nPhone : +256393240576 / +256751700559\r\n[gdlr_core_space height=\"-13px\"]\r\nEmail : info@pashaadventures.co.ug\r\n[gdlr_core_space height=\"20px\"]\r\n[gdlr_core_icon icon=\"fa fa-facebook\" size=\"18px\" color=\"#ffffff\" margin-left=\"\" margin-right=\"20px\" link=\"https://www.facebook.com/Pashaadventures/\" link-target=\"_blank\"] [gdlr_core_icon icon=\"fa fa-twitter\" size=\"18px\" color=\"#ffffff\" margin-left=\"\" margin-right=\"20px\" link=\"#\" link-target=\"_blank\"]\";s:6:\"filter\";b:1;s:6:\"visual\";b:1;}i:11;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:555:\"[gdlr_core_space height=\"-20px\"]\r\n[gdlr_widget_list title=\"Why Book With Us?\" title-color=\"\" background-color=\"\" color=\"\" border-color=\"\" ]\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>[gdlr_core_icon icon=\"fa fa-dollar\" size=\"15px\" color=\"#ffa127\" margin-right=\"13px\" ]Value for your money  guaranteed</li>\r\n<li>[gdlr_core_icon icon=\"fa fa-headphones\" size=\"15px\" color=\"#ffa127\" margin-right=\"10px\" ]Customer care available 24/7</li>\r\n<li>[gdlr_core_icon icon=\"fa fa-star\" size=\"15px\" color=\"#ffa127\" margin-right=\"10px\" ]Tailor-made Tours & Activities</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n[/gdlr_widget_list]\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;s:6:\"visual\";b:0;}i:12;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s: