:\"\";s:7:\"content\";s:1481:\"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are safari tour operator based in Uganda and very passionate about East Africa - its nature, wildlife, landscape and cultural diversity. Our trademark is to design personalized, tailor-made and detailed itineraries for individual and group travelers, specializing in luxurious and fly-in safaris, although we also create itineraries for camping and self-drive tours. Adventure travel is our passion! Come and experience Uganda in Africa!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"> Our dedicated staff will insure that you will be satisfied with just the best service that you can expect from a touring company, we always will make sure that our tourists will leave with more than just a smile. From enquiring for your unforgettable experience, to the day that we bid you farewell and a speedy come back, our friendly service and staff will be one of the things well remembered. Be insured that we will always be there to assist you in any which way possible and make sure that you won’t be in need of anything.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"> Let us tantalize your traveling senses with the unparalleled splendor that only the Uganda’s National Parks can offer. Coupled to arguably the most sought after bird species like the Shoe bill stork, and so many other wildlife species of animals and plants. Offering day trips in the parks and relaxing evenings under the stars and the roaring of Lions, this will be your traveling dreams come true.</p>\";s:10:\"text-align\";s:4:\"left\";s:24:\"apply-the-content-filter\";s:7:\"disable\";s:9:\"font-size\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"content-font-weight\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"content-letter-spacing\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"content-text-transform\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"text-color\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"padding-bottom\";s:4:\"30px\";}}i:1;a:3:{s:8:\"template\";s:7:\"element\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"text-box\";s:5:\"value\";a:11:{s:2:\"id\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"content\";s:1625:\"<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"> <strong>Why choosing us </strong></h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\">We provide an unrivalled choice of quality escorted tour packages to East .Africa packed with exciting daily sightseeing highlights and features. Our safari offers a variety of activities in Rwanda, Uganda, Kenya, Tanzania and Congo, such as safaris, city tours, white water rafting, boat trips, fishing trips, horseback riding, community walks, mountain climbing, Gorilla trekking, Cultural tours, domestic flight bookings, honey moon safaris, beach holidays and more.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Tours is a company operated by people who have been involved in Travel and Wildlife Safaris since childhood, people who were raised in and have traveled through the remote regions of Africa and beyond. We would like to share our passion for Africa with you, its wildlife, culture, and outstanding scenery. With our wide diversity of expertise we will plan every aspect of your African holiday / vacation, ensuring you a very personal experience. We specialize in tailor made safaris for families, small groups of friends, and the single traveler to Uganda, Tanzania, Kenya, and Rwanda.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Safari offers the most exciting, personal and reliable tours through East Africa. We are experts in the field of East Africa`s wildlife and culture and offer great value for money tours that are safe and comfortable. Choose from one of our many itineraries or create your own personal safari. Whatever you may require we will strive to provide. Join us now for your true African Safari.</p>\";s:10:\"text-align\";s:4:\"left\";s:24:\"apply-the-content-filter\";s:7:\"disable\";s:9:\"font-size\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"content-font-weight\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"content-letter-spacing\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"content-text-transform\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"text-color\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"padding-bottom\";s:4:\"30px\";}}}}i:1;a:3:{s:8:\"template\";s:7:\"wrapper\";s:4:\"type\";s:10:\"background\";s:5:\"ite